TO INSTALL:

NodeJS >= 0.6.5
SASS >= 3.1.11 (http://sass-lang.com/download.html)

http://npmjs.org/
Mac OS X: $ (sudo) npm install haml

Ubuntu 10.10: sudo apt-get install libhaml-ruby1.8
Fedora 14:    yum install rubygems
              gem install haml

TO BUILD:

$ cd build
$ node build.js

or for production mode

$ node build.js production
